  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      139.29,
      289.25,
      378.49,
      312.59
    ],
    "text": "BE it enacted by the Parliament of the Democratic SocialistRepublic of Sri Lanka as follows:\u2014",
    "fonts": [
      "Times"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      139.29,
      325.25,
      378.58,
      360.59
    ],
    "text": "1.This Act may be cited as the Fiscal Management(Responsibility) (Amendment)Act, No. 13 of 2016, and shallbe deemed to have come into operation on January 1, 2016.",
    "fonts": [
      "Times",
      "TimesNewRoman,Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      139.29,
      373.25,
      378.54,
      420.59
    ],
    "text": "2.Section 3 of the Fiscal Management (Responsibility)Act, No. 3 of 2003 is hereby amended in paragraph (e)thereof by the substitution for the words and figures\u201c7 per centum;\u201d of the words \u201cten per centum;\u201d.",
    "fonts": [
      "Times",
      "TimesNewRoman,Bold",
      "TimesNewRoman,Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      139.29,
      435.65,
      378.46,
      458.99
    ],
    "text": "3.In the event of any inconsistency between the Sinhalaand Tamil texts of this Act, the Sinhala text shall prevail.",
    "fonts": [
      "Times",
      "TimesNewRoman,Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
